        <mxCell id="RIRhulhHAlF5B4grZ4R7-30" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Требования:&lt;br&gt;Фильтрация сотрудников по Табельному номеру:&lt;br&gt;- [ТН] + [&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Есть на КПС, нет на КПД]&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;- [ТН] + [&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Квалификация не соответствует]&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;- [ТН] + [&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Квалификация &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;ско&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;ро истечет] (+60 дней от даты истечения квалификации КПС)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Ограничения:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;В данную подборку не должны попасть записи, где:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;ТН +&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Номер протокола +&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Дата протокола&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; +&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Область аттестации&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; +&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Результат&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; = Заполнено.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
